MX Revolution Cordless Mouse
----------------------------

Global

* Scroll Wheel: Free spin
* Scroll Wheel Button: Middle Click
* Thumb Wheel Forward -> cmd+shift+]
* Thumb Wheel Backward -> cmd+shift+[
* Thumb Wheel Button -> Nothing

HipChat

* Settings from Global
* Thumb Wheel Forward -> ctrl+page up
* Thumb Wheel Backward -> ctrl+page down

Skype

* Settings from Global
* Thumb Wheel Forward -> cmd+opt+left arrow
* Thumb Wheel Backward -> cmd+opt+right arrow
